Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't…give…in…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garganta is opening up…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're in a bad situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuginomai Hakuren!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodeno…shirayuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are others who've\Ncome to help, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you guys waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Soul Reapers\Naren't the only ones here…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that those people\Nare everyone's Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't the Zanpakuto\Nin rebellion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain, Sodenoshirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kurotsuchi undid the mind\Ncontrol over the Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We apologize for\Nthe turmoil we caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will work hard to make it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Roar!\N– Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear in Frenzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the idea of going ahead\Nof your master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, master shmaster,\Nit doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how ugly it is\Nto rush to get the credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to get that\Nbeing jealous of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,getting beaten to the punch\Nis far more ugly…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai, Tsukishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Cero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let those hot-blooded\NZanpakuto do the job alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no such intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just taking care of\Nwhat needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shunko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if your careless\Nattacks damage the town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kurosaki's still inside there…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to\Nget rid of that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our priority is the Hollows\Nthat surround us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people check for Ichigo\NKurosaki's Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to find out how he is\Ndoing inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much,\NCaptain Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But our enemy's\Nnumbers are so great…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we faced them\Ntogether with our Zanpakuto,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're still going to be\Ndifficult to handle…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this very moment,\NCaptain Kurotsuchi continues to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}release the remaining Zanpakuto\Nfrom the mind control,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there's not enough time to wait\Nfor them to rendezvous with us…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me confirm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of\Nall of the ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey… Weren't those two…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…they had us\Ncompletely fooled…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.\NWe're in the middle of a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know…I get it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how Hozukimaru feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even put on a hokey act
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by claiming he wouldn't\Naccept Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason,\Nit doesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be\Ntalking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sort out your feelings\Nlater, at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, right now,\Nwe have a mission as Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your personality change after
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mind control was undone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the Zanpakuto\Nthat feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we are members of the same\NThirteen Court Guard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have no intention of\Nbeing bound by the mission…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of my business\Nhow you people feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's also my right\Nto think what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you're not going to say\Nyou've reached your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with only injuries like those,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Town has been\Nplaced in an Area Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now free to use full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "full power"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get carried away\Nand commit a blunder,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're not cleaning up after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want someone\Nwith a big butt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cleaning up after you,\Nright, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you such a dummy\Nlike your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, in fact, he is a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut that out, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…let me say this, Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who want to give you a \Npiece of their mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, I…I…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for\Ntrying to play it cool…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Omaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll show those guys that\Nthey're no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash'em! Gegetsuburi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it you!\NWhat'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you\Nhaven't been released
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Muramasa's mind control!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicking your beloved master\Nin the back like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Address me as "Mister."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Smash'em,\NMister Gegetsuburi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Soul Reaper addresses\Nhis own Zanpakuto with "Mister"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– when doing a Shikai?!\N– Uh, excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! Make history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Don't talk nonsense!\N– This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were\Nbeing so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you won't\Naddress me with "Mister"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That grazed me a bit…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I took too much rest…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body seems a bit slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep wasting your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll take care of\Neverything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the least you can do is to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfrom getting caught in my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir… We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I dribbled…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense Ichigo's\NSpiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sense\Njust waiting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take measures fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa's Spiritual Pressure\Nis out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with a captain's Bankai,\Nit won't be easy to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unless we do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are more of them\Nstill coming out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to have to face\Nall of them, as well, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this makes\Nso much extra work…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is no time\Nto be arguing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Times like this are the only time\Nyou two get along, it seems…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get\Nanywhere like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure\Nof the sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has increased even further…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inducing the fissure to\Nexpand and attracting Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, infinite flow of\NMenos will come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that fissure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can seal it,\Nthat should help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you going to\Nseal something that big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fissure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.\NMore is about to flow out…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What immense\NSpiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In his depleted condition…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that power\Ncoming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using his Spiritual Pressure\Nto force them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be possible with\Nimmense Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he is one reckless dude…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,\Nhe needed our power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my…am I beat…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because you're\Nolder than you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLet's take care of the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!\NIs it still expanding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kurosaki?\NCan he be saved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we can't get near it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to leave\Nthe rest to Ichigo himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that calls for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Let's settle everything\Nonce and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already left for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about before…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt you really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, use me all you\Nwant as your good Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying all\Nthose nasty things to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you believe\NI'd really say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You're an idiot!\N– Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,